---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'Terms of Service — Easy1099Tax';
const description = 'Terms of Service for Easy1099Tax. The calculator provides estimates for informational purposes only and is not professional tax advice.';
const updated = 'June 2, 2026';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Acceptance of terms</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">By accessing or using Easy1099Tax (the "Service"), you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Not professional advice</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Easy1099Tax provides <b>estimates for general informational and educational purposes only</b>. It is not, and must not be relied upon as, tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice. Tax laws are complex and change frequently, and your individual circumstances may produce materially different results. Always consult a qualified tax professional and the IRS before making financial or tax decisions.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Accuracy and estimates</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We base calculations on current, authoritative sources (IRS, SSA, and published inflation adjustments) and use the final 2025 and 2026 federal figures, but we make no warranty that results are accurate, complete, or current. Tax rules change, and the calculator currently estimates federal taxes only — it does not include state or local income taxes.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">To the fullest extent permitted by law, Easy1099Tax and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of, or reliance on, the Service or its results. You use the Service at your own risk.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Acceptable use</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">You agree not to misuse the Service, attempt to disrupt it, or use it for any unlawful purpose.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We may modify the Service or these Terms at any time. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Questions about these Terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@easy1099tax.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline">hello@easy1099tax.com</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
